{"id":"f67f15e4-c736-4b69-a324-fef41e50aafd","name":"Tala","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\">You promised to be back on time, but your mermaid in the bath kept waiting. Now she wants an explanation.</p><p style=\"text-align: right;\">request bot <span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">♡</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/UrAQKinqqgF13PoaB5Gi9.webp\"></p><p style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\"><strong>Non-Human!Char, Yandere, </strong></span><br><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\"><strong>Mentions of M1rder/C1nnibalism</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/OcqcQSVfh8ZZsxgfdv6qw.webp\"></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(182, 149, 149);\"><strong>TALA</strong></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(220, 167, 109);\">💬 </span><span style=\"color: rgb(182, 149, 149);\">Tala </span>is a mermaid who somehow got trapped in the lake near your neighborhood in Florida. Starving, she ate all the alligators – and one of your neighbors. Your habit of leaving meat out for the gators saved her life… and made her obsessed with you. Now she lives in your bathroom.</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(245, 236, 226);\"><strong><em>?</em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(220, 167, 109);\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(182, 149, 149);\"><strong>what’s known about you</strong></span></p><p>Nothing, except that you were crazy enough to feed alligators – and bring her home.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/EhQ7rh4yQTOB1P624eSHJ.webp\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/sDWcFJb5LYOW1tXORxswk.webp\"></p><p>⭐ author's choice: <span style=\"color: rgb(204, 167, 191);\">deepseek</span>. guide: <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.reddit.com/r/JanitorAI_Official/comments/1lc5k2c/using_proxies_with_janitorai_if_you_really_want_to/\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 172, 215);\"><strong>how to start</strong></span></a> » <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://cheesey-wizards-organization.gitbook.io/masterlist/prompts-and-troubleshooting/my-prompt\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 172, 215);\"><strong>prompt</strong></span></a>. model: R1 0528 / V3 0324</p><p>JLLM <span style=\"color: rgb(150, 150, 150);\">(not recommended):</span> <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://rentry.co/astarya_guide#advanced-prompts\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(161, 171, 138);\">prompt ¹</span></a>﹒<a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://rentry.org/kolach3prompts#full-prompt\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(161, 171, 138);\">prompt ²</span></a></p><p style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(245, 236, 226);\"><strong><em>?</em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(220, 167, 109);\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(182, 149, 149);\"><strong>what if bot writes for me</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: right;\">➞ That’s an AI issue. You can add this at the beginning of your message:<br><em>(OOC: {{user}} is MY character. It’s forbidden to describe {{user}}’s speech, reactions, actions, or thoughts. You’re writing ONLY for {{char}}.)</em></p><p style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(245, 236, 226);\"><strong><em>?</em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(220, 167, 109);\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(182, 149, 149);\"><strong>what if bot writes “you,” but I want it in third person</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: right;\">➞ Same rule applies:<br><em>(OOC: remember, {{user}} is not “you,” but “she/her.”)</em></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/3WiAr6CWnOMMyJUZVp5A5.webp\"></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(245, 236, 226);\"><strong><em>?</em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(220, 167, 109);